Form & Layout:

Rounded rectangular container with soft corners and balanced proportions
Horizontal, layered structure with clear grouping of elements
Tight, efficient spacing with strong alignment across a single grid

Visual Style

Dark, desaturated background with a subtle gradient
Light foreground elements for contrast without harsh brightness
Thin borders and soft shadows to separate the panel from the background
Minimal visual noise — every element feels intentional

Elements

Mix of small icon buttons and compact input areas
Controls use consistent sizing, padding, and corner radius
Buttons appear as subtle toggles rather than heavy components
One visually stronger action element to anchor the composition
Prefer icons and visual cues over text wherever possible

Typography

Clean, modern sans-serif
Use text sparingly — only where essential
Primary text slightly brighter; secondary text muted

Interaction Design

Designed for speed and efficiency
Focus states are understated but visible (soft glow or border shift)
Hover/active states are minimal, relying on slight contrast changes

Overall Feel

Lightweight, precise, and utilitarian
Prioritizes clarity and flow over decoration
Feels like part of a larger system rather than a standalone component
Optimized for frequent use without drawing attention to itself